                2. **內容策略 (Content)**: What type of posts do they use?
                3. **破局建議 (How to Win)**: How can I differentiate?
              `,
              config: { tools: [{ googleSearch: {} }] }
          });
          setCompAnalysis(res.text || '無法分析');
      } catch (e: any) {
          alert(`分析失敗: ${e.message}`);
      } finally {
          setIsCompAnalyzing(false);
      }
